data.description: Enjoy over 3500 sq ft in this stunning, newer construction craftsman by Eastwood Homes. The main floor is bright and open with an eat-in kitchen overlooking the living room w/ custom stone fireplace and two-story wall of windows for extra light. Entertain guests with ease in the dining room and kitchen connected by bar area with white cabinets, sleek gray backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops.   This home has TWO master bedrooms! The first floor master suite is spacious w/ separate shower, hi-tech jetted tub, dual vanity & walk-in closet, convenient to nearby main floor laundry room w/ sink and built-in cabinets plus powder room for guests. The top floor offers a second huge master suite w/ custom shelving in the walk-in closet, and bathroom with separate shower and large soaking tub, as well as three large secondary bedrooms with jack and jill bathroom and dual vanity. The expansive unfinished daylight basement provides an incredible opportunity to customize and create additional living space tailored to your needs. The backyard gently slopes down to a large, flat wooded area for maximum privacy. Enjoy the view from the deck off the main level or the terrace level porch. Video Tour available.
